    "description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">At 8th level, choose one benefit from the following:</p><h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Boon of Fury</strong></h4><p dir=\"ltr\">Your weapon attacks deal extra damage equal to your Wisdom modifier. In addition, you can infuse divine power into a weapon attack to deal an extra 1d8 damage, the type of which is the same as you deal with Channel Divinity: Elemental Intervention. Once you have used this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier, you can&rsquo;t do so again until you finish a long rest.</p><h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Furious Spellcraft</strong></h4><p dir=\"ltr\">Damage you deal with Cleric cantrips increases by your Wisdom modifier. You also learn a bonus cantrip chosen from your elemental school (from any class&rsquo;s spell list).</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
